e-523-stored-cross-site-scripting-via-comments","description":"WordPress before 5.2.3 allows XSS in stored comments.","date":"2019-09-05"}],"impact":[]},{"uuid":"cab6a4e101fff707911452905151bfe9bf84e1d0fdf9f8d76ce742d717e37e55","name":"4.6.10","description":null,"source":[{"id":"CVE-2019-16220","name":"CVE-2019-16220","link":"https:\/\/www.cve.org\/CVERecord?id=CVE-2019-16220","description":"[en] In WordPress before 5.2.3, validation and sanitization of a URL in wp_validate_redirect in wp-includes\/pluggable.php could lead to an open redirect if a provided URL path does not start with a forward slash.","date":"2019-09-11"}],"impact":{"cvss":{"version":"3.1","vector":"CVSS:3.1\/AV:N\/AC:L\/PR:N\/UI:R\/S:C\/C:L\/I:L\/A:N","av":"n","ac":"l","pr":"n","ui":"r","s":"c","c":"l","i":"l","a":"n","score":"6.1","severity":"m","exploitable":"2.8","impact":"2.7"},"cvss3":{"version":"3.1","vector":"CVSS:3.1\/AV:N\/AC:L\/PR:N\/UI:R\/S:C\/C:L\/I:L\/A:N","score":"6.1","severity":"medium","av":"network","ac":"low","pr":"none","ui":"required","s":"changed","c":"low","i":"low","a":"none","exploitable":"2.8","impact":"2.7"},"cwe":[{"cwe":"CWE-601","name":"URL Redirection to Untrusted Site ('Open Redirect')","description":"The web application accepts a user-controlled input that specifies a link to an external site, and uses that link in a redirect."}]}},{"uuid":"cab6a4e101fff707911452905151bfe9bf84e1d0fdf9f8d76ce742d717e37e55","name":"4.6.10","description":null,"source":[{"id":"4605594228ee3e14acd82f44ccb154214609bfc9","name":"WordPress Core < 5.2.3 - Open Redirect","link":"https:\/\/www.wordfence.com\/threat-intel\/vulnerabilities\/wordpress-core\/wordpress-core-523-open-redirect","description":"In WordPress before 5.2.3, validation and sanitization of a URL in wp_validate_redirect in wp-includes\/pluggable.php could lead to an open redirect.","date":"2019-09-05"}],"impact":[]},{"uuid":"c8fbc682931fc278f5927875b33c7352d3ae35a3e37763850bddf9d6bb2ccd01","name":"4.6.10","description":null